(firstQuint)Acupuncture for Primary Insomnia.

 Acupuncture is potential to be an alternative treatment for primary insomnia.

 The purpose of this study is to evaluate the clinical effectiveness of acupuncture treatment on primary insomnia.

 This is a randomized single-blinded controlled trial.

 Patients will be randomly assigned to the electro-acupuncture group or the placebo acupuncture group.

 Patients will be put into groups and then compared.

